This is a string program to calculated MEP(minimiun energy path).

I edited the original code distributed by Amit Samanta and Weinan E et al.
I change the parts of calculating error ,energy calculation and force calculation. It can calculate the MEP of numerical PES.


usage are presented in my blog:
http://chen-xin.tk/blog/index.php/archives/21/


more details about string please see:
http://web.math.princeton.edu/string/string0_MEP.html
